{"TopicId":128816,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"How to link to an image in sig","CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-29T02:07:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-29T02:07:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHI all,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0As the title says, how can I link another forum post to an image in my signature?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! Oh, pressing the link icon does nothing. Its an imgur image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-29T02:43:17Z\u0022 title=\u002212/29/2015 02:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 29, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Majorjim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaarst","CreatedById":126740,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-29T02:21:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInsert the image as usual, then double click on it: this will give you a few options including adding a link to the image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-29T03:28:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222339981\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128816\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221451355668\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022126740\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gaarst\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Gaarst said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInsert the image as usual, then double click on it: this will give you a few options including adding a link to the image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat did it, thanks mate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}